COMPILATION
===========

+ To compile the program for debugging, use

  make debug

+ To compile the program with optimizations turned on, use

  make release

+ To clean all intermediate files and the executable, use
  
  make clean

+ You must clean all files before switching between debug and relase.


USAGE EXAMPLES
==============

+ To get help on the available options, use

  ./run.x -?

+ As a small example, try

  ./run.x -w 40 -h 30 -s 10 -v


